Package: PowerR
Title: Simulation-based Power Analysis for Experiment Planning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Asiri", "Ediriwickrema", , "asiri.e@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application and supporting R functions for
    simulation-based power analysis across common biomedical experiment
    designs: t-tests (two-sample/paired/one-sample), two-proportion
    tests, one-way ANOVA, log-rank survival, and limiting dilution
    analysis (LDA) under a Poisson single-hit model.
